snippet: President Mwai Kibaki of Kenya vetoed huge bonuses that Parliament members quietly awarded themselves last week after protests and public outcry over the action.
abstract: Kenyan Pres Mwai Kibaki vetoes $109,500 bonuses that Parliament members awarded themselves after protests and public outcry over the action.
lead_paragraph: President Mwai Kibaki of Kenya vetoed huge bonuses that Parliament members quietly awarded themselves last week after protests and public outcry over the action.

headline.seo: Kenya: President Mwai Kibaki Vetoes Parliament Bonus
